<html><body><span style="padding-left:150px;"><h4>Nexmo Gateway  Instruction Process</h4></span><br><ul><li>If User has an existing Nexmo account then login into account by clicking on the following link <a style="color:blue;font-weight:bold;" target="_blank" href="https://dashboard.nexmo.com/sign-in">Click here</a>. <b>--(this will be a link button which will be redirected to the Nexmo login page)</b></li><li>If a User does not have any Nexmo account then he first needs to Signup with Nexmo by clicking on the following link <a style="color:blue;font-weight:bold;" target="_blank" href="https://dashboard.nexmo.com/sign-in">Click here</a> providing the Valid mobile number. Once the account has been created just login into Nexmo account.</li><li>After clicking on the <b>API Settings</b> on top-right corner of the Page <b>Key</b> and <b>Secret</b> values will be displayed.</li><li>Copy that Key and Secret values from your Nexmo account and paste it in the<b>API Key</b> and <b>API Secret</b> fields textbox in your salesforce Organisation.</li><li>In the <b>From</b> field textbox User will be providing the Registered mobile number with Nexmo account.</li></ul></body></html>